pylipd.lipd module

The LiPD class describes a LiPD (Linked Paleo Data) <https://cp.copernicus.org/articles/12/1093/2016/cp-12-1093-2016.html> object. It contains an RDF <https://www.w3.org/RDF/> Graph which is serialization of the LiPD data into an RDF graph containing terms from the LiPD Ontology <http://linked.earth/Ontology/release/core/1.2.0/index-en.html> How to browse and query LiPD objects is described in a short example below, while this notebook <https://nbviewer.jupyter.org/github/LinkedEarth/pylipd/blob/master/example_notebooks/pylipd_tutorial.ipynb> demonstrates how to use PyLiPD to view and query LiPD datasets.

class pylipd.lipd.LiPD[source]

Bases: object

The LiPD class describes a LiPD (Linked Paleo Data) <https://cp.copernicus.org/articles/12/1093/2016/cp-12-1093-2016.html> object. It contains an RDF <https://www.w3.org/RDF/> Graph which is serialization of the LiPD data into an RDF graph containing terms from the LiPD Ontology <http://linked.earth/Ontology/release/core/1.2.0/index-en.html> How to browse and query LiPD objects is described in a short example below.
